[Episode 7]

2
00:00:39,420 --> 00:00:40,500
Grandpa.

3
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:41,193
Dad.

4
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:45,100
Wait a moment, Dongdong.

5
00:00:45,940 --> 00:00:48,027
The company's
high-level meeting will be held

6
00:00:48,027 --> 00:00:49,500
at the boathouse tomorrow.

7
00:00:50,180 --> 00:00:51,220
Zhiqiang.

8
00:00:51,227 --> 00:00:51,660
Yes.

9
00:00:51,900 --> 00:00:52,940
Chuxue.

10
00:00:52,940 --> 00:00:53,620
Chunyan.

11
00:00:54,180 --> 00:00:55,727
You may rest at home.

12
00:00:55,727 --> 00:00:57,727
Just send a servant
to go with me will do.

13
00:00:57,740 --> 00:00:58,500
Yes, Mr. Shangguan.

14
00:00:58,900 --> 00:00:59,940
Who do you want to take?

15
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:01,260
I'll take this girl.

16
00:01:05,627 --> 00:01:06,427
Grandpa,

17
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:07,827
this doesn't seem appropriate.

18
00:01:07,827 --> 00:01:09,827
Perhaps it's because
you haven't been feeling well recently,

19
00:01:09,827 --> 00:01:11,827
the company is in chaos now.

20
00:01:11,827 --> 00:01:12,760
Moreover,

21
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,160
this is such an important occasion.

22
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,660
She's just a servant.

23
00:01:15,727 --> 00:01:17,493
Should you reconsider your choice?

24
00:01:19,260 --> 00:01:20,540
I've tolerated you all for a long time.

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:22,620
I know what you're thinking.

26
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:25,360
I don't have many days left.

27
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:27,760
You're all hoping for my early demise,

28
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,960
so that one of you
can become the chairman,

29
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:30,460
and another can become
the general manager.

30
00:01:30,540 --> 00:01:31,380
This

31
00:01:31,740 --> 00:01:33,293
is what you wish for, right?

32
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:35,460
Dad, please don't be angry.

33
00:01:35,660 --> 00:01:37,780
Chuxue is just thinking for the company.

34
00:01:37,780 --> 00:01:39,140
We'll follow your arrangement.

35
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:41,900
Get the car ready.

36
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:42,780
Yes, Mr. Shangguan.

37
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,140
Come here.

38
00:01:50,727 --> 00:01:52,493
Take good care of Mr. Shangguan.

39
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,693
It seems everyone cares about you a lot.

40
00:01:57,780 --> 00:02:00,420
I advise you
not to overstep your bounds.

41
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:11,493
Just wait and see.

42
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:15,620
Come, let's all sit down.

43
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:20,560
Let me introduce you

44
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:22,060
to the top management
of the Shangguan Group,

45
00:02:22,060 --> 00:02:23,093
Wang Tianye.

46
00:02:25,380 --> 00:02:26,260
In the company,

47
00:02:26,260 --> 00:02:27,660
he's in charge of all matters,

48
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:29,627
big and small.

49
00:02:30,027 --> 00:02:32,827
He's been a loyal worker of the group
for many years.

50
00:02:32,893 --> 00:02:33,727
Dongdong,

51
00:02:34,027 --> 00:02:35,727
why don't you introduce yourself?

52
00:02:37,620 --> 00:02:38,700
Hello, everyone.

53
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:39,780
My name is Feng Dongdong.

54
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:41,580
I'm a servant of

55
00:02:41,580 --> 00:02:42,327
the Shangguan family.

56
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:48,493
Hello, Dongdong.

57
00:02:48,493 --> 00:02:49,860
Nice to meet you.

58
00:02:52,460 --> 00:02:53,460
Why did you

59
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:54,927
train Mu Feng to be

60
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,493
like a servant?

61
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:58,780
Some matters

62
00:02:58,780 --> 00:03:00,860
can be left to the assistant to handle.

63
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:01,693
In front of you,

64
00:03:01,693 --> 00:03:02,960
we're all servants.

65
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:05,827
Mu Feng,

66
00:03:05,827 --> 00:03:06,727
how old are you now?

67
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:07,527
I'm twenty-two.

68
00:03:07,527 --> 00:03:08,927
I heard that you help a lot

69
00:03:08,927 --> 00:03:10,427
with Tianye's work.

70
00:03:10,427 --> 00:03:11,360
Have you thought

71
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,493
of coming to help me?

72
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:15,100
With my abilities,

73
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:17,180
I can only be my father's assistant.

74
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:19,093
Being your father's assistant

75
00:03:19,093 --> 00:03:20,427
is wasting your talents.

76
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:24,727
I know his capabilities very well.

77
00:03:24,727 --> 00:03:26,740
If it weren't
for his past position with Xiao,

78
00:03:26,893 --> 00:03:28,427
he would have retired long ago.

79
00:03:28,827 --> 00:03:29,893
That's settled then.

80
00:03:30,340 --> 00:03:31,327
Come and help me.

81
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:33,360
Yes.

82
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:34,760
Mu Feng, do you understand?

83
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:37,860
Great.

84
00:03:37,860 --> 00:03:39,620
I'm also going to the company
to do something with Dongdong.

85
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:41,060
Both of you

86
00:03:41,220 --> 00:03:42,327
should get to know each other.

87
00:03:44,220 --> 00:03:44,820
Mr. Shangguan,

88
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:47,527
isn't it inappropriate
for Mr. Wang's son

89
00:03:47,527 --> 00:03:48,860
to accompany a servant?

90
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:49,493
Do you

91
00:03:49,493 --> 00:03:50,740
have a say here?

92
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:58,220
It's an honor for Mu Feng to have tasks

93
00:03:58,260 --> 00:03:59,527
assigned by Mr. Shangguan.

94
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:03,427
Have a walk with me.

95
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:04,740
Mu Feng.

96
00:04:06,580 --> 00:04:07,900
Spend more time with Dongdong.

97
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:22,760
Your first step is done;

98
00:04:22,893 --> 00:04:24,927
Mr. Shangguan already knows who you are.

99
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:27,020
The next step is

100
00:04:27,020 --> 00:04:29,620
to get close to Wang Tianye's
most trusted person.

101
00:04:32,220 --> 00:04:32,980
Have a seat.

102
00:04:40,580 --> 00:04:42,500
You must be finding
this situation strange.

103
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:44,460
As a servant of the Shangguan family,

104
00:04:45,293 --> 00:04:47,460
how could I be treated equally
as your father and the others?

105
00:04:47,740 --> 00:04:49,300
Mr. Shangguan surely
has his own arrangements.

106
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:04,547
[Life is Drama]
